data.description: Contact Ryan Andrews at RE/MAX Horizon Realty 307-351-1145 to see! Seller is offering a $5,000 credit for closing costs or discount points! Welcome to your ideal family home! This beautifully updated 5-bedroom, 2.5 bath residence features spacious living areas, a detached garage with backyard access, a gardening shed, and a generous corner lot with a large front yard. The home boasts a large master suite, as well as a back porch perfect for grilling. Tasteful updates have been made, making it move-in ready!,Located in a prime neighborhood close to schools, parks, shopping, and dining. Don't miss this opportunity to make it yours! In addition to all the family space, a bonus space with a separate entrance is located in the front of the home prime for a home based business, home gym, or a work-from-home office!
